The '''Orange Lady''', also known simply as '''The Lady''', was a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] located in the [[Corellian Sector (Nar Shaddaa)/Legends|Corellian Sector]] of [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]]. It was owned by the [[Besadii]] [[Kajidic/Legends|kajidic]] and tended by [[Hopper]].<ref name="LoNH" /> [[Ziv Banks]] died in a shootout there.

